<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169735>
    bibo:endPage "54" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "43" ;
    bibo:volume "1036" ;
    dc:creator "Çinar, Melih Ertan" ;
    dc:date "2005" ;
    dc:title "Syllis ergeni: a new species of Syllidae (Annelida: Polychaeta) from Izmir Bay (Aegean Sea, eastern Mediterranean Sea)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169737>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169738>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169739> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169737>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Syllis ergeni. A. Anterior end, holotype MNCN 16.01 / 10261. B. Anterior falcigers, holotype. C. Middle falcigers, holotype. D. Posterior falcigers, holotype. E. Dorsal simple chaeta, holotype. F. Ventral simple chaeta, holotype. G. Aciculae on anterior parapodia, paratype ESFM­ POL / 04 ­ 183. H. Aciculae on middle parapodia, paratype. I. Aciculae on posterior parapodia, paratype. J. Proventriculus and pharynx, paratype. Scale line A 440 µm, B ­ F 38 µm, G ­ I 36 µm, J 930 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169737/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169738>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Syllis ergeni. — A. Dorsal view of body, holotype MNCN 16.01 / 10261. — B. Anterior end, paratype ESFM­POL / 04 ­ 183. — C. Opening of pharynx, paratype. — D. Anterior­lateral view, paratype. — E. Glands on dorsum of anterior segments, paratype. — F. Proventriculus, paratype. Scale line A 440 µm, B 664 µm, C 218 µm, D 135 µm, E 21 µm, F 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169738/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169739>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Syllis ergeni, paratype ESFM­POL / 04 ­ 172. — A. Specimen with stolon. — B. Lateral view of stolon. — C. Anterior end of stolon. — D. Anterior end of stolon. Scale line A 1000 µm, B 566 µm, C, D 285 µm. The specimen was stained with ShirlastainA (brown stain) (Figs. A and C) to clear appendages of the stock and stolon." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169739/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

